{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by luck, two or three of our friends came into this cafe-- it was [NON-ENGLISH]-- two or three of our friends came in at that time, and they came and sat with us instead of with them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They all knew-- they knew them equally as well as they knew us, but they happened to choose us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was there with this Jewish boy, and having a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and I don't know the other-- the man who made the remark eventually, I think, left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not so much, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- you knew, and in fact, the only people who knew that the war was going to go the way it did, and-- and things were that bad and all were the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were telling-- and the writers, the Jewish writers were predicting exactly what was going to happen and all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think a lot of them had read 'Mein Kampf.'",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very-- I couldn't wait every day to get a newspaper, and it became a big issue, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just before the-- just before the war broke out, it was a big issue, and I-- we were making plans with a number of our friends of what they were going to do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was going to-- That's where I got the idea originally of marrying different girls, you know, to get them American papers and all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but nothing happened then, because everybody kept thinking, oh, maybe it'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But believe me, it wasn't all right in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
